provincialism
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the political system of control by Provinces as distinct from central Government (1856-1878?)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: the system of provincial government as opposed to attitude of provincialism
